data.description: The spectacular sunset skies glow in nearly every direction, and they are delightfully enjoyed from most rooms and and most of the decks at 111 Summer Pl Dr. From the stunning skies to the soothing water, this home includes views of the ocean and the sound. Though it's not a waterfront home, it comes with the gorgeous water views, along with easy ocean access and the sound access just steps away. Located in North Topsail Beach between the ocean and the sound, this well situated home encourages you to enjoy the beauty of outdoor living in NC. The yard is large and fully fenced with an awesome firepit. There's a bar setup under the deck for laid back weekend gatherings, and tons of decks. A two car garage is a dream for parking spacing and beach gear storage. Inside is light and bright with a spacious kitchen and three bathrooms. The open floor living room, dining room, and kitchen are surrounded by windows and water views. The primary bedroom and bathroom are particularly large and luxurious. 3 complete bedrooms make for a good amount of sleeping space, but there's also an unfinished 4th bed and bathroom downstairs, ready to be added.Additionally, this dreamy home has an update roof, hardi siding, updated floors and bathroom, and a new HVAC. This home would be good for a permanent residence or a rental home for an income property.
